OL,3,CFunding cuts may put children's rights
OL,4,Cin jeopardy, commissioner warns
OL,6,FJersey's Children's Commissioner is
OL,7,Fwarning of serious consequences if the
OL,8,FGovernment lowers its budget in 2026.
OL,10,FDr Carmel Corrigan explains that
OL,11,Fproposed cuts could threaten the
OL,12,Foffice's ability to ensure the island
OL,13,Fcomplies with UN standards for
OL,14,Fchildren's rights.
OL,16,FShe adds: "We are potentially subject
OL,17,Fto budget cuts in 2026, in addition to
OL,18,Fwhat we have had in 2025, but we are
OL,19,Fnegotiating and in discussions with
OL,20,Fgovernment officials and ministers.
