OL,3,CFunding cuts may put children's rights
OL,4,Cin jeopardy, commissioner warns
OL,6,F"The Government has a statutory
OL,7,Fobligation to adequately resource us,
OL,8,Fthat is in the law.
OL,10,F"If we cannot fulfil our statutory
OL,11,Fduties because of funding, then our
OL,12,Findependence is going to be under
OL,13,Fthreat, and our independence is
OL,14,Fcrucial to what we do.
OL,16,F"It is what allows us to be critical,
OL,17,Fto question and investigate on behalf
OL,18,Fof children."
