OL,6,FDemand for places at the secure
OL,7,FGreenfields site significantly rose in
OL,8,Fthe last quarter of 2024, resulting in
OL,9,Fthe facility increasing its registered
OL,10,Fcapacity from three to six places by
OL,11,Fthe end of the year.
OL,13,FThere were 14 notifications of secure
OL,14,Fplacements, with a small number of
OL,15,Fchildren being placed in Greenfields
OL,16,Fon more than one occasion.
